commit_message:
Fix two errors in functional test

1. create_policy method only accept name and spec as input parameters.
This patch fixes incorrect usage in functional test;
2. Profile and policy type name now includes version number;

After applying this patch, functional test should work correctly.

Change-Id: Id477785375199a099727a0ef49f773f62f0f5957
